equation: V.signalSource.offset + (if time < V.signalSource.startTime then 0.0 else V.signalSource.height)
assert(1.0 + R1.alpha * (R1.T - R1.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(1.0 + R2.alpha * (R2.T - R2.T_ref) >= 1e-15, "Temperature outside scope of model!");
assert(R1.T_ref >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R1.T_ref, has value: " + String(R1.T_ref, "g"));
assert(R1.T >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R1.T, has value: " + String(R1.T, "g"));
assert(R1.T_heatPort >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R1.T_heatPort, has value: " + String(R1.T_heatPort, "g"));
assert(R2.T_ref >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R2.T_ref, has value: " + String(R2.T_ref, "g"));
assert(R2.T >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R2.T, has value: " + String(R2.T, "g"));
assert(R2.T_heatPort >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= R2.T_heatPort, has value: " + String(R2.T_heatPort, "g"));
assert(c5 >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= c5, has value: " + String(c5, "g"));
assert(C5.C >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= C5.C, has value: " + String(C5.C, "g"));
assert(c4 >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= c4, has value: " + String(c4, "g"));
assert(C4.C >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= C4.C, has value: " + String(C4.C, "g"));
assert(c3 >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= c3, has value: " + String(c3, "g"));
assert(C3.C >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= C3.C, has value: " + String(C3.C, "g"));
assert(c2 >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= c2, has value: " + String(c2, "g"));
assert(C2.C >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= C2.C, has value: " + String(C2.C, "g"));
assert(c1 >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= c1, has value: " + String(c1, "g"));
assert(C1.C >= 0.0, "Variable violating min constraint: 0.0 <= C1.C, has value: " + String(C1.C, "g"));
